    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, showing no signs of rear subframe fatigue, and is complemented by a factory strut tower brace. This collector-grade specimen boasts flawless paint depth and a pristine interior, offering a pure mechanical connection and peak naturally-aspirated performance.",
