    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-fresh appearance and performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied annually. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the original scent of high-end materials persists. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the precision climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists. The engine bay is pristine, and the driving experience is whisper-quiet and incredibly responsive. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning buyer. Included are all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover.",
