      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, delivering a linear power band with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous manifold pressure response. This example features a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. With zero mechanical deficiencies and a chassis that retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the serious collector seeking mechanical purity.",
